{"title": "One of One", "slug": "one-of-one", "date": "2021-08-01", "author": "theline1", "excerpt": "", "categories": ["News On The Line"], "featuredImage": "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/nft-4.jpg", "images": ["https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/0x3b3ee1931dc30c1957379fac9aba94d1c48a5405_66374-1.webp", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-3.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/churchill.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-3.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.11.27-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.11.27-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/mint-face-logo-small-2.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/nft-3.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.11.27-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.11.27-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/0x3b3ee1931dc30c1957379fac9aba94d1c48a5405_66374-1.webp", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png"], "content": "<p>One of one means there's one artwork and one owner. Simple. When you purchase the artwork, you get to be the only person on the planet that decides what happens to it next. You might decide to:</p><p>Hang it on your Digital Wall at home with a <a href=\"https://www.nftculture.com/nft-displays/nft-display-frame-review-samsung-frame-tv/\">frame screen</a>. </p><p>Add it to your Twitter tabs in Chrome with <a href=\"https://nametag.org\">NameTag</a>.</p><p>Resell it on an open marketplace like <a href=\"https://opensea.io\">Opensea</a>.</p><p>This week we again share an artist we like, a MintFace sale of note and a 1:1 artwork you might like to consider adding to your collection.</p><h3 id=\"mintface-artist-feature\">MintFace Artist Feature</h3><p>Jeneva is a 3D artist with her work available across <a href=\"https://t.co/yqoZ1U5a3H?amp=1\">Rarible</a>, <a href=\"https://t.co/51nLn45RME?amp=1\">Foundation</a> (since April) and <a href=\"https://t.co/4uskQNqBbB?amp=1\">Showtime</a> marketplaces. I discovered Jeneva recently through this tweet that resonated with how many of us feel when we put art into the world.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Every day I discover new talented authors and sometimes I feel mediocre comparing myself to them. But at the same time, it gives me the motivation to keep working and improve my skills.<br /><br />Good morning wonderful people ✨Have a great day!✨❤️</p>&mdash; Jeneva (@jenevaNFT) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jenevaNFT/status/1421764209734529027?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 1, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>Jeneva has created a character called MDM. </p><blockquote>\"MDM symbolizes the fact that nothing is perfect and it is imperfections that make us who we are and create our individuality.\"</blockquote><p>Jeneva's work apply a different treatment to MDM that, when placed side by side, shows the variations of who we are just beneath the surface. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/0x3b3ee1931dc30c1957379fac9aba94d1c48a5405_66374-1.webp\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"667\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/0x3b3ee1931dc30c1957379fac9aba94d1c48a5405_66374-1.webp 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/0x3b3ee1931dc30c1957379fac9aba94d1c48a5405_66374-1.webp 667w\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://rarible.com/jeneva\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"590\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.20.11-AM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><h3 id=\"mintface-sale-feature\">MintFace Sale Feature</h3><p>Abi Daker recently sold their first hand drawing of an <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@abidaker/aerial-drawing-of-venice-53865\">aerial view of Venice</a> on the Foundation marketplace. Abi hand draws each illustration in freehand line and shade illustration that is then converted into a digital artwork. </p><p>Abi has expanded on the series with every digital artwork including a large size printable file.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I just listed “New York City Financial District Panorama” for sale on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/withFND?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@withFND</a>! 🌐<br /><br />In many ways, I think this is one of the best <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/drawings?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#drawings</a> I ever made. I love it! It would look great either printed or on a massive screen :)<a href=\"https://t.co/fl2EsU4P9J\">https://t.co/fl2EsU4P9J</a></p>&mdash; Abi (@abidaker) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/abidaker/status/1418137762956468224?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 22, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>I've left the best until last. Abi Daker's work is featured on real currency. The £5  note in the United Kingdom includes his hand drawn view of Westminster and the Elizabeth Tower from the South Bank looking across Westminster Bridge. <br /><br /></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/churchill.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"350\" height=\"286\"></figure><p>The provenance and authenticity of his art makes his <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@abidaker/st-paul-s-cathedral-63469\">hand drawn St Paul's Cathedral work</a> currently available on Foundation, even more hypnotising. Maybe it's just me though... after living in London for 8 years and walking to work past St Paul's Cathedral I have to see I'm a little biased.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-3.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1196\" height=\"1680\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-3.jpg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/nft-3.jpg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-3.jpg 1196w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"mintface-artwork-feature\">MintFace Artwork Feature</h3><p>Alejandro Cartagena is the artist of the series <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@AlejandroCartagena-Assembly\">The 50 Carpoolers</a> available on the Foundation marketplace. Carpoolers was done during one year, from 2011-2012 looking over a bridge on a highway. All the Carpoolers have been sold by Alejandro with some now available for resale on the secondary market.</p><blockquote>\"Humbled and thankful to all my collectors for changing my life in a beautiful way. You’ve empowered a committed artist to be free!\" Alejandro Cartagena.</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.11.27-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1082\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.11.27-AM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.11.27-AM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.11.27-AM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-02-at-10.11.27-AM.png 2304w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Major congrats! 🎉<br />Photographer Alejandro Cartagena <a href=\"https://twitter.com/halecar2?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@halecar2</a> set a few records with his &quot;50 Carpoolers&quot; series this week: <br /><br />📸 45 NFTs collected<br />📸 173 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24ETH&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$ETH</a> (~$412K USD) earned <br />📸 800+ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24ETH&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$ETH</a> total bid volume and 332 bids<br />📸 20 live auctions at once!  <br /><br />↳ <a href=\"https://t.co/bKRCdbVF1O\">https://t.co/bKRCdbVF1O</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/5W3MH1oVGR\">pic.twitter.com/5W3MH1oVGR</a></p>&mdash; Foundation 🌐 (@withFND) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/withFND/status/1421258372507078660?ref_src=t\nwsrc%5Etfw\">July 30, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>Alejandro feels a sense of responsibility to the art he puts into the digital art world and that is one reason why I'm keeping an eye on what Alejandro might create next. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Exactly Reuben. But the people that imagined this space worked to build it. We must work to build our work into it and not just use it as a dumpsite. We need to be responsible as artists. We are just getting started. Happy to be on this ride with you 🤝🤝 <a href=\"https://t.co/LJTYayG2sA\">https://t.co/LJTYayG2sA</a></p>&mdash; alejandro cartagena (@halecar2) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/halecar2/status/1421508777568874497?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 31, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>If this article has made you curious about getting started with digital art, we also run the <a href=\"https://maven.com/cache/nft-digital-artist-economy\">Digital Artist Economy workshop</a> helping artists create their first digital art through a <a href=\"https://maven.com/cache/nft-digital-artist-economy\">three week programme.</a> Share it with an artist you'd like to see on an NFT marketplace.</p><p><strong>MintFace surfaces great artists and artworks so you don't have to. </strong></p><p><em>Enjoying MintFace? Help keep it free by supporting the platform in one of two ways.</em></p><p><strong>Art Collectors</strong> - you can become a member to receive a secret weekly MintFace  surfacing artwork that others have missed. No apes. No punks. Just quality art by quality artists.</p><p><strong>Artists</strong> - you can send any notes of appreciation to <strong><em>mintface.eth</em></strong>  in whatever form you feel reflects your art.</p><p><strong>What have you been Mintfacing this week? </strong></p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/businesskiwi\">Share with me on Twitter</a> and I'll mention the best on MintFace. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/mint-face-logo-small-2.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"72\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/mint-face-logo-small-2.png 600w\"></figure><p></p>"}